{"tid":1221698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】日本 2,500 人澀谷集會支持香港人","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T16:01:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0e33cca144331fc628c62498ed83348f5db5c9","tid":1221698,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Af1Z8PHPIq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAf1Z8PHPIq0&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=c64bf01e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Af1Z8PHPIq0</a><br />\n<br />\n日本澀谷昨日約 2,500 人舉行反送中集會。參加者除日本人和香港人外，亦有不少台灣人。他們高叫「香港加油」的口號，又唱《海闊天空》，希望表達與港人連成一線的意願。<br />\n<br />\n昨夜集會於晚上 9 點至 10 點在東京澀谷忠犬八公像前廣場舉行。發起人為前日本社運團體 SEALDs 成員、今年 27 歲的研究院生元山仁士郎。他在 2014 年傘運後，曾多次與香港社運界交流。集會目的在與香港人共同進退，抗議香港政府強行通過修例，以及警察濫權。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 上，日本人以 #TOKYOantiELAB 連結反送中消息。透過社交網絡，主辦方表示聚集到約 2,500 人，當中約有三分一為香港留學生，此外亦有許多日本人，以至台灣人。集會人士以日語、國語、廣東話高叫「香港加油」，並一齊唱 Beyond 的《海闊天空》。有人在高舉的標語上直接使用「反送中」一詞。他們呼籲日本民眾支持香港人，共同站起來為人權、民主戰鬥，又批評香港警察過度使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jpn5_pL5bp_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjpn5_pL5bp_1200x0.png&h=1085bfef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元山表示，「在香港被催淚彈和橡膠子彈攻擊的，與我們同樣都是學生。我們在這裡有集會自由、言論自由，香港現在也為這些自由戰鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n同日傍晚，元山仁士郎又與約 300 人前往東京的香港商務及經濟發展局辦事處，亦舉行抗議集會，舉起「守護香港自由」等標語，為香港的抗爭者吶喊加油。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jpn2_arDXN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjpn2_arDXN_1200x0.png&h=1067371f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-2-500-%E4%BA%BA%E6%BE%80%E8%B0%B7%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%AD%8C-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%A9%BA-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-2-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BE%2580%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=0654400b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-2-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BE%2580%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=8b41a447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-2-500-%E4%BA%BA%E6%BE%80%E8%B0%B7%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%AD%8C-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%A9%BA-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"e7645b509932b90fb8663174820acedf39c0fd74","tid":1221698,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（請大家廣傳民陣fb呼籲！）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣反送中遊行</span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<br />\n遊行終點：政府總部"},{"pid":"d8a1bbe6f8f278602a619c6ab31647cce5ea8065","tid":1221698,"uid":21708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7895c0718caf82799a88e4b6204d7fa81dda6a0","tid":1221698,"uid":194785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da2a6ae7fe7b072b363e663bc8c499